,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fd56ff2d00e3a5aae23a69dd60b6911beab050","tid":1243464,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"affc054c00362cf6dacd7b264b4a6a077414387e","tid":1243464,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqbDT85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqbDT85.jpg&h=c1642c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqHvLgt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqHvLgt.jpg&h=3fc16009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係唔係青衣居民聯會嘅會員全部都有資格做漁農界選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"如果可以 不如整合下唔同屆別一次過攻陷佢!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:06:43.000Z","msg":"應該要先了解下有幾多連登仔係住青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20111206/15866085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20111206%2F15866085&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=cd58c6cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20111206%2F15866085&h=9839fccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20111206/15866085</a><br />\n<br />\n僅159選民 卻擁60席<br />\n在選委會有60席的漁農界，今屆只有159個選民，是三十多個選委界別中最少選民組別之一，且所有選民全是團體選民，漁農界的個體戶根本無票可投。雖然選民團體個個名目不同，卻有少至十幾個團體全屬新界社團聯會的屬會，包括離島區漁農副業協會、港九漁民聯誼會有限公司及香港漁民互助社等，換言之，單是新界社團聯會已在該界別霸佔十幾票。<br />\n最離奇是選民包括部份與漁農界無關的團體，荃灣居民聯會在會內增設「漁民組」，藉此登記為漁農界選民；青衣居民聯會在選民登記冊內，甚至沒有像荃灣居民聯會般以「漁民組」名義申請，卻又同時成功過關為選民。這兩個地區組織，同是新界社團聯會屬會。<br />\n本報致電青衣居民聯會理事長、候任葵青區議員羅競成，但他身在內地未能聯絡；副理事鄧瑞華被問及聯會與漁農界關係時說了句「哦，我揸緊車」，就掛斷電話。"},{"pid":"4f3b44b10cb1d412bdf78b09eb4d3238d8f858f1","tid":1243464,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"諗多左，咪咁天真，人地唔會比你入會架"},{"pid":"1d489bcb57034c160f3ada076e63c6949a35b6ee","tid":1243464,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f3b44b10cb1d412bdf78b09eb4d3238d8f858f1","tid":1243464,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"諗多左，咪咁天真，人地唔會比你入會架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb1b0032129e2898aacba74ec396ecdecfedef7","tid":1243464,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ede106467d93c8700061ab2d2f230f2c1657363e","tid":1243464,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"affc054c00362cf6dacd7b264b4a6a077414387e","tid":1243464,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqbDT85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqbDT85.jpg&h=c1642c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqHvLgt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqHvLgt.jpg&h=3fc16009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係唔係青衣居民聯會嘅會員全部都有資格做漁農界選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:51:20.000Z","msg":"香港花奔業總會<br />\n可以留意是否可以攻陷？"},{"pid":"89e1a683ead303aae4137ba5ab393cc37e24e9f6","tid":1243464,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"看看哪個可以司法覆核，他們入會資格！<br />\n例如香港花奔業總會？"}]}